vote.title: A resolution authorizing approval of an Interlocal Agreement between the City of Dallas and Dallas County, approved as to form by the City Attorney, for Parkland Health & Hospital System to implement a universal Newborn Nurse Home Visit Program as seen in Exhibit A, with matching funds to be provided by Dallas County - Not to exceed $2,000,000.00 - Financing: Coronavirus State and Local Fiscal Recovery Fund
